y\n* {{flagicon|Spain}} Fran - Retired\n* {{flagicon|Brazil}} Mauro Silva - Retired\n\n==RCD Espanyol==\nIn:\n*{{flagicon|Uruguay}} Walter Pandiani - Signed from Birmingham City F.C.\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Luis Garc\u00eda - Signed from RCD Mallorca\n*{{flagicon|Mozambique}} Armando S\u00e1 - Signed from Villarreal CF\n*{{flagicon|Argentina}} Zabaleta - Signed from San Lorenzo de Almagro\n*{{flagicon|Brazil}} Costa - Signed from Olympique de Marseille\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Jofre - Signed from Levante UD\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Riera - Signed from Girondins de Bordeaux\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Ito - Signed from Real Betis\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Juanfran - On loan from Real Madrid\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Hurtado - Return from Eibar\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Iraizoz - Return from Eibar\n\nOut:\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Soldevilla  - Transferred to Polideportivo Ejido\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Jonathan Soriano - On loan to UD Almer\u00eda\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Toni Velamaz\u00e1n - Transferred to UD Almer\u00eda\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Morales - Transferred to Gimn\u00e0stic de Tarragona\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Riera - On loan to Manchester City F.C.\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} H\u00e9ctor - On loan to Racing de Ferrol\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Carlos Garc\u00eda - On loan to UD Almer\u00eda\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Serrano - On loan to Racing de Santander\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Mi\u00f1ambres - Return to Real Madrid\n*{{flagicon|Argentina}} Maxi Rodr\u00edguez - Transferred to Atl\u00e9tico de Madrid\n*{{flagicon|Argentina}} Hugo Benjam\u00edn Ibarra - Transferred to Boca Juniors\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Bertran - Transferred to C\u00e1diz CF\n*{{flagicon|Belgium}} Erwin Lemmens - Transferred to  Olympiacos\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} \u00c0lex Fern\u00e1ndez - Transferred to  Xerez CD\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Dani - Transferred to Olympiacos\n*{{flagicon|Romania}} Raducanu - Transferred to FC Vaslui\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Ra\u00fal Molina - Transferred to Rayo Vallecano\n*{{flagicon|Spain}} Amavisca - Retired\n\n== Getafe CF==\nIn:\n* {{f