ool Stage]]\n| rowspan=\"6\" |{{Sortname|Paul|McGregor|Paul McGregor (rugby league)}}\n|{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|9\n|{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|182\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/seasons/nrl-2015/st-george-illawarra-dragons/summary.html|title=NRL 2015 - St George Illawarra Dragons - Rugby League Project|website=www.rugbyleagueproject.org|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|-\n![[2016 St. George Illawarra Dragons season|2016]]\n|[[2016 NRL season|NRL]]\n|24\n|10\n|0\n|14\n|341\n|538\n|11/16\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|[[2016 NRL Auckland Nines|Pool Stage]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|{{Sortname|Kurt|Mann}}\n|10\n|{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|133\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/seasons/nrl-2016/st-george-illawarra-dragons/summary.html|title=NRL 2016 - St George Illawarra Dragons - Rugby League Project|website=www.rugbyleagueproject.org|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|-\n![[2017 St. George Illawarra Dragons season|2017]]\n|[[2017 NRL season|NRL]]\n|24\n|12\n|0\n|12\n|533\n|450\n|9/16\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|[[2017 Auckland Nines|Pool Stage]]\n|{{Sortname|Jason|Nightingale}}\n|16\n|{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|191\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/seasons/nrl-2017/st-george-illawarra-dragons/summary.html|title=NRL 2017 - St George Illawarra Dragons - Rugby League Project|website=www.rugbyleagueproject.org|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|-\n![[2018 St. George Illawarra Dragons season|2018]]\n|[[2018 NRL season|NRL]]\n|24(2)\n|15(1)\n|0\n|9(1)\n|519(60)\n|472(31)\n|7/16\n|Semi Final\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{Sortname|Matthew|Dufty}}\n|13\n|{{Sortname|Gareth|Widdop}}\n|205\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/seasons/nrl-2018/st-george-illawarra-dragons/summary.html|title=NRL 2018 - St George Illawarra Dragons - Rugby League Project|website=www.rugbyleagueproject.org|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|-\n![[2019 St. George Illawarra Dragons season|2019]]\n|[[2019 NRL season|NRL]